Yeeeaaaaa so yesterday was a long blur of a day answering preseason posts, I apologize for misreading Token as Chest somehow....wasn't even the first one smh.....

{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}} 


So to clarify, you didn't get a token because it was ARAM. Those matches don't give tokens, well....because you didn't *actively* pick him. It could have been a lucky coincidence you did so well, but overall ARAM just has too many different playstyles and scenarios that it wouldn't be right to grade them the same way other matches are graded.
